Method Detail

doubleIterator

public DoubleIterator doubleIterator()
Compute a fresh DoubleIterator, which can be used to provide test data of type double. The DoubleIterator returned should be freshly created. Usually it should not be at its end. However, in rare cases it might make sense to have an empty iterator be computed (e.g., by filtering).
